My magic code is the combination of HTML, CSS, and JavaScript that I use to generate stunning websites with advanced animations. Here's a sneak peek at my template:
```html
<!-- HTML Structure -->
<div class="container">
  <header class="header">
    <nav class="nav">
      <!-- Navigation Menu -->
    </nav>
  </header>
  <main class="main">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="hero">
      <h1 class="hero-title">Welcome to my website</h1>
      <p class="hero-subtitle">Where magic happens</p>
    </section>
    <!-- Features Section -->
    <section class="features">
      <h2 class="features-title">What I can do</h2>
      <ul class="features-list">
        <!-- List of features -->
      </ul>
    </section>
  </main>
  <footer class="footer">
    <!-- Footer Content -->
  </footer>
</div>

<!-- CSS Styles -->
<style>
  /* Global Styles */
  body {
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
  }
  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 20px;
  }
  /* Hero Section Styles */
  .hero {
    background-image: linear-gradient(to bottom, #f7f7f7, #fff);
    padding: 50px;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .hero-title {
    font-size: 36px;
    font-weight: bold;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  .hero-subtitle {
    font-size: 18px;
    color: #666;
  }
  /* Features Section Styles */
  .features {
    padding: 50px;
  }
  .features-title {
    font-size: 24px;
    font-weight: bold;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  .features-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }
  .features-list li {
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  /* Footer Styles */
  .footer {
    background-color: #f7f7f7;
    padding: 20px;
    text-align: center;
  }
</style>

<!-- JavaScript Code -->
<script>
  // Add event listener to navigation menu
  document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function() {
    const nav = document.querySelector(".nav");
    nav.addEventListener("click", function() {
      // Toggle navigation menu
    });
  });
</script>
```
This is just a basic template, and I can customize it to fit your needs. What type of website would you like me to create?

